text: haey ke teangpir neak ban ttuoltean phlechheu noh srab te pheap akrat robsa ke teangpir kaban leatatradeang champoh ke teang pir haey ke teangpir ban beh sloekchheu thansuokr yk mk betbang leu reangkay robsa ke teangpir . haey a dam ban thveu khosa nung batobanhchea nei mcheasa robsa ke ning ban v nge v ng( pi karpit)
